## Toolchain commands (used by hooks and the Implementer agent)

These are the commands the Quality Gate hook (`validate-implementation.sh`) and the Implementer subagent will run. Override the defaults below by exporting these env vars in your shell, in `direnv`, or in CI.

| Variable          | Purpose                  | Example for this project           |
| ----------------- | ------------------------ | ---------------------------------- |
| `TEST_CMD`        | Run a specific test file | `npx vitest run`                   |
| `TEST_ALL_CMD`    | Run the full test suite  | `npm test`                         |
| `TYPECHECK_CMD`   | Static type checking     | `npx tsc --noEmit`                 |
| `LINT_CMD`        | Linter                   | `npx eslint`                       |
| `FORMAT_CMD`      | Formatter                | `npx prettier --write`             |
| `BUILD_CMD`       | Production build         | `npm run build`                    |

